high_descs: Turn around and go to the right side of the desk.
Pick up the set of keys on the desk on the left side.
Take the keys to the nightstand in between the two beds.
Set the keys on the nightstand.
Go to the shelf by the foot of the bed.
Pick up the set of keys on the shelf.
Go to the nightstand between the two beds.
Set the keys down on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on the nightstand.

high_descs: Step forward, then turn right and walk forward, turn left and go to the desk.
Pick up the keys on the left side of the desk.
Turn around and walk to the bedroom. Walk forward into the space between the two beds.
Place the keys in front of the clock on the nightstand.
Turn around, walk forward, then turn left and walk to the storage cubbies.
Pick up the keys in the top right compartment.
Return to the nightstand in between the two beds.
Place the keys on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Pick up two sets of keys in the house and place on nightstand.

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk towards the wall, hang a left and walk up to the wooden desk.
Pick up the leftmost set of keys off of the wooden desk.
Turn around and walk around the partition into the other room, continue to the nightstand that is in between the two beds.
Put the keys on the front edge of the nightstand.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk up to the wooden shelving unit on the wall.
Pick up the set of keys off of the upper right shelf.
Walk back over to the nightstand in between the two beds.
Put the set of keys on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Move two sets of keys to a nightstand.
